Frog-leather boots are a piece of frog-leather armour that can be bought from Reldak's Leather Armour in the market place of Dorgesh-Kaan. Frog-leather armour cannot be created through the Crafting skill.

Wearing the boots requires level 25 in Defence and Ranged.
